OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780834280
OL,3,CKing appoints composer and engineer as
OL,4,COrder of the Thistle members
OL,6,FAdditionally, Baroness Katherine
OL,7,FGrainger was appointed the Usher of
OL,8,Fthe Green Rod, marking her as an
OL,9,Fofficer of the order.
OL,11,FThe order is comprised of 16 knights
OL,12,Fand ladies, as well as the Queen, The
OL,13,FPrincess Royal, the Duke of Rothesay
OL,14,Fand The Duke of Edinburgh.
OL,16,FSir Jim is known for his work in
OL,17,Fengineering and university leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
