PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780834280
OL,3,CKing appoints composer and engineer as
OL,4,COrder of the Thistle members
OL,6,FHe was appointed as the Rolls-Royce
OL,7,Fchairman in electrical power systems
OL,8,Fat the University of Strathclyde in
OL,9,F1993, later becoming head of the
OL,10,Felectronic and electrical engineering
OL,11,Fdepartment in 2003, and then principal
OL,12,Fand vice-chancellor in March 2009,
OL,13,Fwhere he remained until he retired in
OL,14,F2025.
OL,16,FHe served as president of the Royal
OL,17,FAcademy of Engineering from 2019 to
OL,18,F2024, the first Scot to hold the
OL,19,Fposition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
