PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780834280
OL,3,CKing appoints composer and engineer as
OL,4,COrder of the Thistle members
OL,6,FHe was knighted in 2012 for services
OL,7,Fto education, engineering and the
OL,8,Feconomy, and was appointed Knight
OL,9,FGrand Cross of the Order of the
OL,10,FBritish Empire (GBE) in 2024.
OL,12,FSir James, a highly renowned Ayrshire-
OL,13,Fborn composer, is known not only for
OL,14,Fhis music, but for achievements
OL,15,Fincluding the establishment of the
OL,16,FCumnock Tryst festival.
OL,18,FHe was awarded a knighthood during the
OL,19,FQueen's Birthday honours of 2015, with
OL,20,Fhis anthem Who Shall Separate Us?
OL,21,Fcommissioned for her funeral in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
