PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780834280
OL,3,CKing appoints composer and engineer as
OL,4,COrder of the Thistle members
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Charles approved
OL,7,Fthe award of the King's Medal for
OL,8,FMusic for Sir James.
OL,10,FBaroness Grainger, a Glaswegian, is
OL,11,Fknown for her achievements in both
OL,12,Fsport and law.
OL,14,FShe won Olympic rowing gold in the
OL,15,Fdouble sculls at London 2012 with team-
OL,16,Fmate Anna Watkins.
OL,18,FRegarded as Britain's most successful
OL,19,Ffemale rower, she is the only woman
OL,20,Facross any sport to win medals in four
OL,21,Fconsecutive Olympic Games.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
