OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780834280
OL,3,CKing appoints composer and engineer as
OL,4,COrder of the Thistle members
OL,6,FBaroness Grainger was made a CBE for
OL,7,Fservices to rowing in the 2013 New
OL,8,FYear Honours.
OL,10,FAfter years of studying law and
OL,11,Fmedical ethics, she completed a PhD in
OL,12,Fthe sentencing of homicide at King's
OL,13,FCollege London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
